{"tid":1809084,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"踏入2020 年，捉鬼成為左抗爭面對嘅首個危機，而呢個危機係致命嘅","createTime":"2020-01-02T23:25:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T00:53:03.000Z","uid":1477,"like":132,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"0e8e1e23be2bd22176ad32e21cd6316fb7fd3291","tid":1809084,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T23:25:38.000Z","msg":"其實捉鬼真係極極極極極極少數<br />\n出黎果103萬人（假設得咁多）<br />\n捉鬼嘅可能得10個人<br />\n但呢十個人做嘅野會被無限放大<br />\n會不斷比人提，不斷比人loop<br />\n搞到好似好撚多人捉鬼<br />\n但其實得極少數人咁做<br />\n當然我都知唔止十個，可能有成百上千<br />\n但一定唔會係大多數人嘅行為<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我地亦應該係捉鬼風氣再次萌芽之際將佢撲滅</span></span><br />\n<br />\n加埋網絡上嘅五毛，弱智仔不斷渲染<br />\n就會將呢極少數嘅事吹噓成<br />\n「好多人捉鬼、嘉年華化、退步、分化、割席」<br />\n其實有出黎嘅人就知<br />\n99.9%見到嘅畫面都係同以往一樣<br />\n可能有啲人的確係柒左，退步左，老人痴呆左<br />\n但絕對唔係網絡上鋪天蓋地咁嚴重<br />\n<br />\n記住由6月9號開始，我地有三大原則<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「不分化，不割席，不篤灰」</span></span><br />\n但同樣記住呢三個原則唔係你唔進步嘅借口<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">望住勇武不斷進步，和理非忍心睇住自己一直都停步不前？</span></span><br />\n落雨要開遮<br />\n和理非要掩護勇武<br />\n呢啲係我地作為和理非嘅責任<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">除左捉鬼，我地可以做多好多野<br />\n哂心機諗可以點捉鬼，不如諗下除左捉鬼，我地有咩可以做到</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">願榮光歸香港</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最後想做個宣傳：有能力嘅人請拒絕幫襯金拱門，貪小便宜嘅代價係有更多嘅手足出事，請支持黃色經濟圈，拒絕無良商家。</span></span>"},{"pid":"edd37b352c9e4fed0cfb81f61c374fa646905acf","tid":1809084,"uid":54014,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T23:33:27.000Z","msg":"幾個月無捉過鬼，突然又出現返哩啲捉鬼風氣。<br />\n而家一個勇武手足都不能少啊，捉錯一個就死一個。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4a474e8ac15fd2971ccec4d008ffe05e66c9910","tid":1809084,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edd37b352c9e4fed0cfb81f61c374fa646905acf","tid":1809084,"uid":54014,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T23:33:27.000Z","msg":"幾個月無捉過鬼，突然又出現返哩啲捉鬼風氣。<br />\n而家一個勇武手足都不能少啊，捉錯一個就死一個。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T23:34:49.000Z","msg":"真係有好多野要做<br />\n而唔係focus 係捉鬼"},{"pid":"4aac8866233ed4ac56a957e61327ae37ead88246","tid":1809084,"uid":131122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"edd37b352c9e4fed0cfb81f61c374fa646905acf","tid":1809084,"uid":54014,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T23:33:27.000Z","msg":"幾個月無捉過鬼，突然又出現返哩啲捉鬼風氣。<br />\n而家一個勇武手足都不能少啊，捉錯一個就死一個。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T23:35:32.000Z","msg":"派便衣警捉鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf38ff56ef3a48a7df5c5469d9a28548b81f738f","tid":1809084,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T23:36:46.000Z","msg":"推！！不捉鬼！"},{"pid":"2663d71466a0cb6ca00f73ef976752eb10115c05","tid":1809084,"uid":1477,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T23:37:35.000Z","msg":"一開po 就兩個負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但又唔留言架喎<br />\n五毛咁早開工？"},{"pid":"6becb54a75ab865faf5a169de57505c3184250c3","tid":1809084,"uid":216800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T00:13:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"04769c207d7d94c812fee1567b789df7245934db","tid":1809084,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T00:16:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4757e0c00c5aa240a30a08e98318b2b2579baee1","tid":1809084,"uid":83910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T00:20:36.000Z","msg":"百萬級遊行可能真係會有小量人未進化<br />\n未熟玩法<br />\n一齊文宣教化多d<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n不分化 不割席<br />\n不篤灰 不捉鬼"},{"pid":"272936b5f1820636150b8246d6036f912f7e9ed0","tid":1809084,"uid":113155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T00:21:29.000Z","msg":"致力文宣防鬼，而非捉鬼。<br />\n鬼就一定有架啦，而家師奶阿叔𡃁妹都可以鬼，點捉？鬼冇樣睇，不如一齊諗下點可以喺有鬼情況下保護自己，再加以文宣。<br />\n捉鬼之心不有，防鬼之心不可無。<br />\n<br />\n例如<br />\n情境1: 有槍有棍嗰啲，大叫：「佢有槍有棍！」<br />\n情境2: 帶耳機（請分清楚耳機和助聽器），上前溫柔提醒：「麻煩手足除耳機，會俾人誤會係鬼架。」<br />\n（致力文宣出街攝衫同不帶耳機文化）<br />\n情境3: 臥狗開始捉人，現場多手足可以上前救人固然好，冇嘅話，街坊請大聲喧嘩：「有賊啊！搶嘢啊！救命啊！」<br />\n<br />\n我淨係諗到哩啲。"},{"pid":"e1f9fce428f33b7b83d1aeadc473c5fec8290516","tid":1809084,"uid":252292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T00:23:03.000Z","msg":"啲人不停提真係好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3b3ad7c6c2ac149789e0a39cff52039f2b4b42e","tid":1809084,"uid":252292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6becb54a75ab865faf5a169de57505c3184250c3","tid":1809084,"uid":216800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T00:13:20.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T00:23:40.000Z","msg":"多謝手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6715126ff1f505fc430c784ea59241b453187dd","tid":1809084,"uid":128151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T00:28:16.000Z","msg":"不捉鬼<br />\n不捉鬼<br />\n不捉鬼<br />\n不捉鬼<br />\n不捉鬼<br />\n大家跟我罰抄十次<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c684f063458ac4e3c8a1cbf67f7840e3a94ead39","tid":1809084,"uid":29555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T00:50:46.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01